==Authorize.Net Test Mode== After initial setup, your Authorize.Net account is placed in test mode by default; you can view a red bar with the warning in the Authorize.Net Merchant Interface. In test mode, Authorize.Net does not process transactions and always returns a successful response. Thus, a test payment never gets charged. {br}
