    &lt;add value="Full_Instance_URL" /&gt;
&lt;/audienceUris&gt;
}}}}
#:In the code shown above, ''Full&#95;Instance&#95;URL'' is the full URL of your Acumatica ERP instance—for example, ''http://app.site.net/instance&#95;name/''.
