Before you import data to or export data from Acumatica ERP, you must define to the Acumatica ERP system the format of the data in the external system or file. For this purpose, you use data providers in the system.{br}
In this chapter, you will find detailed information on data providers and will learn how to create data providers for the external data. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_6404d8fd-dce0-4a06-836b-6c43e56c96aa] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__con_Import_and_Export_Scenarios|Import and Export Scenarios] *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__con_Data_Providers|Data Providers]
| *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__how_Create_CSV_Data_Provider|To Create a CSV Data Provider] *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__how_Create_Excel_Data_Provider|To Create an Excel Data Provider] *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__how_Create_MS_SQL_Data_Provider|To Create a Microsoft SQL Data Provider] *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__how_Modify_Data_Provider|To Modify a File Data Provider] *[HelpRoot_Integration\IS__how_Link_Provider_to_Existing_File|To Link a File Data Provider to an Existing File]
