Returns a numeric expression, rounded to the specified precision (''decimals'').{br}

Example: {{=Round(([Price]-[Cost])/[Cost], 2)}}{br}

Here {{[Cost]}} and {{[Price]}} are used in a function argument, and ''2'' is the number of decimal places.
