| [anchor|#_03208a34-3962-49de-9916-f331d4f0e24c]
Returns the current date in the user&rsquo;s time zone. The system extracts the user&rsquo;s time zone from one of the following sources, which are ordered by priority from the highest to the lowest:[anchor|#_0cf72585-0ebc-4e09-8c46-dbcb3d5227cc]
